636
00:44:09,635 --> 00:44:17,762
Teachers learned to utilize study island questions and developed fall winter screener exams for grades six, seven, and eight.

637
00:44:18,642 --> 00:44:29,731
Administrators and teachers reviewed behavioral interventions and developed their own pyramid to determine what is considered tier one, tier two, and tier three.

638
00:44:30,492 --> 00:44:33,915
The Andrews and the McGlynn schools met at Medford High.

639
00:44:34,930 --> 00:44:50,695
